                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Chatting w/ Nitay trying to figure non-redeploy of &lt;del&gt;ROOT&lt;/del&gt; and .META., it struck us that state transition code is distributed all over master and that execution on state change needs to be coalesced if any chance of a global understanding.  We thought too that general state better maintained over in zk so states-in-transition ride over change of master, etc.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
